These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, avocado
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | broccoli   | avocado   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, parkour
1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   |
| Sport      | parkour | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, punk
1. the person eating kiwi is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | lettuce | kiwi |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | punk     |

 #################################

 
